1) apply stylesheet for each file: xmlstarlet tr XSLT_FILE XML_FILE_INPUT 
   scripts/apply_single_stylesheets.sh
2) concat (removing header for each file)
3) apply global stylesheet
4) convert xml to json with java
5) flat json with json_flattenizer.html, and "download" the new flatten json
6) clear flatten, using shell script (to improve)
6) convert flatten json to csv
